1
00:01:36,123 --> 00:01:40,123
=Joy of Life Special Edition=

2
00:01:40,123 --> 00:01:43,043
=Episode 2=

3
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,200
Master Fei, we've checked.

4
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,120
The inn is safe.

5
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:50,799
Good. Then we'll rest here.

6
00:01:50,799 --> 00:01:51,439
Yes.

7
00:01:56,719 --> 00:01:58,120
I will walk around

8
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,000
to see if there's anything strange.

9
00:01:59,439 --> 00:02:00,319
OK.

10
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,080
I know you'll follow me.

11
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,240
Where did you get this?

12
00:02:16,599 --> 00:02:18,280
I took it from a fruit ranch nearby.

13
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,560
Where are you going?

14
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,439
Beiqi.

15
00:02:24,639 --> 00:02:25,360
Beiqi?

16
00:02:25,879 --> 00:02:27,800
Don't they always want to go to war with us?

17
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:28,800
The war is coming.

18
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,000
The Investigator's Office established
an intelligence network

19
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,400
in Beiqi years ago.

20
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:34,319
The performance was bad. They need a head.

21
00:02:34,639 --> 00:02:35,319
So they send you there?

22
00:02:35,919 --> 00:02:38,120
Me? I'm only good at poisoning others.

23
00:02:39,479 --> 00:02:40,240
I'm seeing someone off.

24
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,199
The one sitting in the carriage?

25
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:44,000
Yes.

26
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:45,879
It's Yan Ruohai's son,

27
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:46,560
Yan Bingyun.

28
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,360
Really a promising young man.

29
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,000
How can you send such an excellent
young man to an enemy country?

30
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,560
It's all because of you.

31
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,319
Because of me?

32
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:57,919
That Teng Zijing you killed is a scout of the Fourth Division.

33
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:02,159
A member of the Fourth Division
actually tried to kill his superior.

34
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:05,080
Yan Ruohai must take the responsibility.

35
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:05,800
Teng Zijing

36
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:08,800
is under the command of his son Yan Bingyun.

37
00:03:09,039 --> 00:03:11,520
The Head was so angry that
he dismissed him from his post,

38
00:03:12,759 --> 00:03:15,439
asking him to disguise with his men as trade caravan

39
00:03:15,439 --> 00:03:17,680
to take over the intelligence network in Beiqi.

40
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,000
It's pretty serious.

41
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:22,000
I'm kind of seeing him off,
and kind of keeping up the formation.

42
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:25,879
I killed a member of our division. Am I in trouble?

43
00:03:26,759 --> 00:03:28,719
Teng Zijing is not a regular member of the Investigator's Office.

44
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,240
He is relatively new to our office.

45
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,199
So it's no big deal.

46
00:03:31,639 --> 00:03:33,560
But you were lucky this time.

47
00:03:34,319 --> 00:03:34,800
What do you mean?

48
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:37,879
The Fourth Division is in charge of detection and patrol.

49
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,080
The Sixth Division is the division responsible for assassination.

50
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:42,759
Whoever wants to kill you didn't try hard enough.

51
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:44,599
The fake order wasn't given to the Sixth Division,

52
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:46,840
so the scout of the Fourth Division took action.

53
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,159
If someone from the Sixth Division took the order,

54
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,039
then you were in real trouble.

55
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:53,039
I didn't know there are so many stories behind.

56
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:57,479
Well, you should go back.

57
00:03:57,879 --> 00:03:58,960
And listen,

58
00:03:59,639 --> 00:04:00,879
next time you take pears,

59
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,840
do pick those big, fatty ones.

60
00:04:04,199 --> 00:04:06,080
Those are much sweeter.

61
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:19,000
Fan Xian.

62
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:21,560
Yan Bingyun.

63
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,079
Do you stop me

64
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:31,040
to avenge Teng Zijing's death?

65
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,120
Teng Zijing didn't deserve to die.

66
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,959
I already killed him. What do you want?

67
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,519
Give me the token for Director-General.

68
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,680
So you want to take it by force?

69
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,279
Give it to me!

70
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,439
Come on!

71
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:53,639
Yan Bingyun.

72
00:04:55,839 --> 00:04:57,560
You should remember the order you've taken.

73
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:59,240
You can't get off the carriage

74
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:02,199
before arriving in Beiqi.

75
00:05:02,839 --> 00:05:05,279
Fan Xian is cruel and mischievous.

76
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,680
If he keeps the token,

77
00:05:07,879 --> 00:05:10,199
the Investigator's Office
as well as Nanqing will be in danger.

78
00:05:10,759 --> 00:05:12,800
If you get off this carriage,

79
00:05:14,279 --> 00:05:16,920
our undercover operation in Beiqi will be ruined.

80
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,120
By then,

81
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,279
you will be the one

82
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,519
who puts Nanqing in danger.

83
00:05:24,199 --> 00:05:25,000
I won't get off the carriage.

84
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,959
You guys! Take his token for me.

85
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:30,920
Whoever moves will be killed immediately.

86
00:05:44,839 --> 00:05:45,720
That's right.

87
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,439
Go back and rest.

88
00:05:47,959 --> 00:05:48,959
We still have a long way to go tomorrow.

89
00:05:49,199 --> 00:05:52,040
Fan Xian, we'll meet again.

90
00:05:53,279 --> 00:05:55,279
He won't be back for a minute.

91
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:21,639
Wait a moment!

92
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,720
Mr. Fan!

93
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,680
It's a long way from Danzhou to the capital city.

94
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,160
You must be tired.

95
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:33,680
Do I know you?

96
00:06:35,279 --> 00:06:38,160
I've admired you for a long time.

97
00:06:38,199 --> 00:06:39,839
It's a pity that I never got the chance to meet you.

98
00:06:40,199 --> 00:06:43,120
Today we finally meet. I feel so honored.

99
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,240
Fine. Let's find a place to talk

100
00:06:45,399 --> 00:06:46,040
some other day.

101
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,839
I'm not available today. I need to get back at once.

102
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:48,560
See you.

103
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,040
Wait a moment.

104
00:06:55,959 --> 00:06:56,959
You want to check me?

105
00:06:57,399 --> 00:06:57,920
Of course not.

106
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:02,000
I have something to show you.

107
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,199
This map

108
00:07:11,759 --> 00:07:14,319
illustrates the scenic spots of the capital city in detail.

109
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,920
You are here for the first time.

110
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,199
It might be useful.

111
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:23,959
Thank you!

112
00:07:26,399 --> 00:07:29,680
Two taels of silver will be enough.

113
00:07:30,079 --> 00:07:31,160
Two taels?

114
00:07:32,279 --> 00:07:33,079
This map

115
00:07:33,079 --> 00:07:34,439
is made of fine paper

116
00:07:35,079 --> 00:07:36,639
and drawn with fine brush and imperial ink.

117
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:38,600
I worked my heart out

118
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,639
to paint it myself

119
00:07:39,639 --> 00:07:40,959
after carrying out repeated surveys and explorations.

120
00:07:41,279 --> 00:07:42,040
Besides,

121
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:44,240
it's the last one left.

122
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:45,879
Only two taels of silver.

123
00:07:46,639 --> 00:07:49,480
It won't even cover

124
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,000
the trips I've taken and the tea I've had.

125
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,319
Two taels of silver! Here you are!

126
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:02,920
Let's go!

127
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:12,279
It's more than two taels!

128
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:25,560
Everyone,

129
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,759
see you later.

130
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,319
Wang,

131
00:08:30,399 --> 00:08:32,320
how many of your crappy maps have you sold?

132
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:35,679
Almost every young man from official families

133
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:37,080
who came a long way to the capital city has bought my map.

134
00:08:38,879 --> 00:08:39,919
Aren't you afraid of being beaten up?

135
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:44,159
For those who are from big families, two taels of silver

136
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,320
are no big deal.

137
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:46,480
Moreover,

138
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:47,960
there're so many cunning foxes

139
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:50,000
in the capital city.

140
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:52,440
I'm also helping them grow up faster.

141
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,279
Thank you! Thank you!

142
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:01,799
Why not tear it up?

143
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,960
It's two taels of silver after all.

144
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:10,120
Walk along this road,

145
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:10,639
and you'll see the Fan mansion.

146
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:13,320
Let's part here.

147
00:09:13,679 --> 00:09:14,159
Are you leaving?

148
00:09:14,799 --> 00:09:16,200
I've told you. When I arrive in the capital city,

149
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,559
I've something personal to deal with.

150
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,000
Thanks for taking me in.

151
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:21,360
We'll probably never see each other again.

152
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:22,639
Come to me if you need anything.

153
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:23,600
I might be able to help.

154
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,440
You are probably unable to protect yourself.

155
00:09:26,919 --> 00:09:28,600
If Liu Ruyu really wants to kill you,

156
00:09:28,639 --> 00:09:29,519
I'm afraid it won't be easy for you

157
00:09:29,519 --> 00:09:30,480
to enter the Fan mansion.

158
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,120
Please don't die.

159
00:09:34,519 --> 00:09:35,720
Even if you die, I won't avenge on your death.

160
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,960
Thanks for your blessings.

161
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:48,840
Let's see how you are gonna kill me.

162
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,240
The guards are needed elsewhere.

163
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:45,399
I'll escort you back home.

164
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:58,399
I was just told that

165
00:10:58,399 --> 00:10:59,679
I can reach the Fan mansion by going straight.

166
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,200
Why do you make a turn?

167
00:11:01,919 --> 00:11:05,000
A carriage turned over in front.
We have to make a detour.

168
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,360
Young Master, I need to answer the call of nature.

169
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,480
Please wait a moment.

170
00:12:08,639 --> 00:12:09,960
What is this temple?

171
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:11,360
Get out!

172
00:12:28,399 --> 00:12:29,320
Having overbearing vitality Qi

173
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:31,120
at such a young age,

174
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:33,120
who are you?

175
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,759
You don't know who I am?

176
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,320
I really don't care.

177
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:40,159
Someone important is praying in the divine temple.

178
00:12:40,679 --> 00:12:43,080
No one shall enter.

179
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:51,679
So I'm not expected.

180
00:13:06,159 --> 00:13:07,320
The man inside the divine temple said

181
00:13:08,399 --> 00:13:10,080
all citizens of Nanqing can worship in the temple.

182
00:13:10,399 --> 00:13:11,159
You can go inside.

183
00:13:11,679 --> 00:13:13,600
But you can only enter the side palace hall,

184
00:13:13,879 --> 00:13:14,919
not the main hall.

185
00:13:15,919 --> 00:13:17,080
What if I don't go inside?

186
00:13:17,399 --> 00:13:20,000
Then just leave. Cut the crap.

187
00:13:36,759 --> 00:13:38,000
What does the temple worship?

188
00:13:38,679 --> 00:13:41,240
Any temple for worshipping is a divine temple.

189
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:43,279
How could you not know that?

190
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:45,799
Divine temple?

191
00:13:47,399 --> 00:13:49,600
When heaven was separated from earth,
giant monsters ran wild.

192
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,919
Master from the divine temple
came to earth with dignity and virtue,

193
00:13:52,399 --> 00:13:53,759
teaching mankind characters and etiquette

194
00:13:53,759 --> 00:13:55,080
and helping mankind cutting mountains and making seas,

195
00:13:55,399 --> 00:13:56,840
thus laying foundation for the human race.

196
00:13:57,799 --> 00:13:59,320
Haven't you learned that from your parents?

197
00:14:02,639 --> 00:14:03,840
Mythology.

198
00:14:11,759 --> 00:14:13,080
You really don't know who I am?

199
00:14:13,679 --> 00:14:15,759
Anyway, don't step into the main hall.

200
00:15:09,759 --> 00:15:10,759
No ambushes.

201
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:14,960
Is it really a coincidence?

202
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,200
No statue of God as I expected.

203
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:33,679
Mythology.

204
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:38,720
For me, I never believe in God.

205
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:41,320
Yet, I don't know

206
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:42,759
how I came to the world.

207
00:15:43,039 --> 00:15:44,399
If there really is a divine temple,

208
00:15:44,799 --> 00:15:46,200
please do send down an envoy

209
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,080
to explain to me.

210
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:48,519
If you give me the answer,

211
00:15:48,679 --> 00:15:49,679
I will do you the favor of

212
00:15:49,679 --> 00:15:50,320
believing in you.

213
00:15:53,519 --> 00:15:55,000
Food and accommodation all covered.
Just think about it.

214
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:32,600
I have a question for you.

215
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:36,519
Are you an assassin?

216
00:16:38,919 --> 00:16:40,120
Not really.

217
00:16:41,639 --> 00:16:43,279
Then, are you sent by the God?

218
00:16:46,399 --> 00:16:47,759
Not really either.

219
00:16:48,919 --> 00:16:49,960
I think you are.

220
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:23,200
Who... who are you?

221
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:30,359
Are you OK?

222
00:17:31,559 --> 00:17:32,000
I'm fine.

223
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:34,400
After vomiting several times, I just get used to it.

224
00:17:40,559 --> 00:17:42,640
My Lady! My Lady!

225
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:49,079
Are you leaving?

226
00:17:52,279 --> 00:17:53,319
Are you with that man of importance

227
00:17:53,319 --> 00:17:54,000
in the main hall?

228
00:18:01,319 --> 00:18:01,799
Hand, please.

229
00:18:27,559 --> 00:18:28,519
I forgot to ask her name.

230
00:19:23,279 --> 00:19:24,440
When did you get back?

231
00:19:24,839 --> 00:19:26,920
Young Master, I've waited for a long time.

232
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:31,160
Follow that carriage!

233
00:19:38,480 --> 00:19:39,480
Where are you going?

234
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:40,160
That way.

235
00:19:40,279 --> 00:19:40,599
Well.

236
00:19:41,480 --> 00:19:42,599
Young Master, aren't we going back the mansion?

237
00:19:42,599 --> 00:19:43,599
Who told you to go to the mansion?

238
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:44,440
Follow that carriage!

239
00:19:44,480 --> 00:19:45,440
Make a turn.

240
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:46,759
Make a turn!

241
00:19:47,279 --> 00:19:47,839
That way.

242
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:48,319
OK!

243
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:54,640
Your Majesty!

244
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:02,519
Who's that young man?

245
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:05,680
He must be the bastard son of
Assistant Minister of Ministry of Revenue

246
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:07,279
from Danzhou.

247
00:20:08,200 --> 00:20:10,519
He's called Fan Xian, I think.

248
00:20:11,599 --> 00:20:12,200
Tell me what you think.

249
00:20:13,519 --> 00:20:15,160
That young man suddenly appeared today.

250
00:20:15,319 --> 00:20:16,079
It was not an accident.

251
00:20:16,359 --> 00:20:17,079
It was...

252
00:20:18,279 --> 00:20:21,039
It was arranged by Your Majesty.

253
00:20:22,039 --> 00:20:23,359
Why should I arrange that?

254
00:20:24,039 --> 00:20:26,200
I dare not guess Your Majesty's intentions.

255
00:20:30,039 --> 00:20:30,440
Speak!

256
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:33,559
Yes.

257
00:20:35,200 --> 00:20:37,279
It's because Your Majesty wanted to see him.

258
00:20:38,519 --> 00:20:40,359
Did Fan Xian kneel down

259
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:42,000
in the side palace hall?

260
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:45,680
I've paid attention.

261
00:20:46,400 --> 00:20:49,279
Fan Xian didn't kneel down in the Qing Temple.

262
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:52,839
Refuse to kneel down before the God.

263
00:20:55,319 --> 00:20:56,720
It tastes bad.

264
00:20:58,400 --> 00:20:59,440
But don't forget to leave

265
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:01,119
two taels of silver.

266
00:21:02,079 --> 00:21:02,440
Yes.

267
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:03,960
Gong Dian.

268
00:21:04,559 --> 00:21:05,039
Yes, Your Majesty!

269
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:08,039
I heard that the Crown Prince gave you a painting,

270
00:21:09,599 --> 00:21:10,680
and you like it very much.

271
00:21:15,559 --> 00:21:18,440
I acknowledge my sin!

272
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:22,599
Let's go back to the Imperial Palace.

273
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:29,000
It's natural for man to have hobbies.

274
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:31,359
That's no sin.

275
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:33,960
I see.

276
00:21:51,519 --> 00:21:54,599
Your Highness, I'm honored to see you.

277
00:21:56,039 --> 00:21:57,720
Haven't I told you before? Haven't I told you before?

278
00:21:57,759 --> 00:21:58,960
We both love calligraphy and painting,

