00:35:56,599 --> 00:35:57,239
Fan Sizhe?
(Same pronunciation with Versace in Chinese)

564
00:35:58,199 --> 00:35:59,440
Father did! What's wrong?

565
00:36:01,360 --> 00:36:02,079
Really nice!

566
00:36:04,480 --> 00:36:05,400
I'm glad he beat you!

567
00:36:09,039 --> 00:36:10,800
I was... Stop drinking!

568
00:36:11,079 --> 00:36:12,840
I was beaten!

569
00:36:13,199 --> 00:36:14,480
When your father come back,

570
00:36:14,480 --> 00:36:15,679
tell him that

571
00:36:15,679 --> 00:36:16,400
you were beaten.

572
00:36:17,079 --> 00:36:18,679
It's useless to tell him.

573
00:36:19,079 --> 00:36:21,119
Dad is the one who asks my elder sister to discipline me!

574
00:36:22,800 --> 00:36:23,599
Ruoruo is the one who beat you?

575
00:36:23,679 --> 00:36:25,400
Yes! Who dare beat me

576
00:36:25,519 --> 00:36:26,639
but her?

577
00:36:27,599 --> 00:36:28,440
Haven't I sent her away

578
00:36:28,440 --> 00:36:29,199
from home?

579
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:30,800
How come she's back?

580
00:36:30,880 --> 00:36:32,000
How can I know?

581
00:36:33,199 --> 00:36:34,920
I don't care.

582
00:36:34,920 --> 00:36:36,320
Anyway, my hand aches now.

583
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:39,199
What can I do to ease you pain?

584
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:41,400
It'll be fine

585
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:42,480
with money on it.

586
00:36:43,639 --> 00:36:44,400
Look at you!

587
00:36:44,599 --> 00:36:45,159
How can you beat that fox

588
00:36:45,159 --> 00:36:46,079
from Danzhou?

589
00:36:47,039 --> 00:36:48,920
I can beat him if I have money.

590
00:36:49,119 --> 00:36:49,519
You!

591
00:37:10,039 --> 00:37:11,320
The handwriting of Zhuang Mohan,

592
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,480
a famous writer from Beiqi.

593
00:37:13,960 --> 00:37:14,840
You like his handwriting?

594
00:37:15,599 --> 00:37:16,400
It's a gift from others.

595
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:26,360
The sword once used by Si Gujian,

596
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:27,719
a great master from Dongyi Town.

597
00:37:27,880 --> 00:37:28,880
The sword of a great master?

598
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:30,119
Really?

599
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:32,320
I don't know. It's also a gift.

600
00:37:32,719 --> 00:37:33,519
Lend me a box.

601
00:37:34,119 --> 00:37:35,519
Take the wooden one in the middle.

602
00:37:39,159 --> 00:37:41,079
Who gave you all these gifts?

603
00:37:42,119 --> 00:37:44,119
Just young ladies from eminent families.

604
00:37:44,440 --> 00:37:44,960
Why?

605
00:37:45,920 --> 00:37:46,920
Asking for updates.

606
00:37:48,239 --> 00:37:49,079
What?

607
00:37:50,039 --> 00:37:51,360
The letters you wrote to me

608
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:52,840
contain many chapters of

609
00:37:52,840 --> 00:37:53,800
the Red Mansions.

610
00:37:54,199 --> 00:37:54,719
The young ladies

611
00:37:54,719 --> 00:37:56,079
who visited me occasionally saw it

612
00:37:56,280 --> 00:37:57,119
and found it marvelous.

613
00:37:57,480 --> 00:37:58,519
Words spread so fast.

614
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:00,519
Now all the unmarried young ladies

615
00:38:00,519 --> 00:38:01,840
in the capital city

616
00:38:02,039 --> 00:38:03,039
are fans of your book.

617
00:38:03,440 --> 00:38:04,880
They give me gifts every day

618
00:38:05,159 --> 00:38:06,039
Asking for updates.

619
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:08,159
Where did you learn

620
00:38:08,719 --> 00:38:09,639
the word "update"?

621
00:38:10,559 --> 00:38:11,599
From your letters.

622
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:12,760
I just borrowed it.

623
00:38:15,519 --> 00:38:16,320
They don't know

624
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:17,199
who wrote the book, right?

625
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:19,320
Do be relieved.

626
00:38:20,079 --> 00:38:21,280
They've no idea that you wrote it.

627
00:38:22,519 --> 00:38:23,719
I've told you so many times.

628
00:38:24,199 --> 00:38:25,320
I really didn't write it!

629
00:38:25,320 --> 00:38:26,679
It was written by a Mr. Cao.

630
00:38:27,360 --> 00:38:29,679
Brother, no need to hide from me.

631
00:38:30,079 --> 00:38:31,159
I've written to grandma.

632
00:38:31,639 --> 00:38:32,400
She said

633
00:38:32,519 --> 00:38:33,800
there's no Mr. Cao

634
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:34,880
in Danzhou.

635
00:38:35,320 --> 00:38:36,119
I know.

636
00:38:36,559 --> 00:38:38,159
you're afraid that popularity

637
00:38:38,159 --> 00:38:39,039
might cause jealousy.

638
00:38:40,039 --> 00:38:40,599
Rest assured!

639
00:38:41,039 --> 00:38:42,400
Your secret is safe with me!

640
00:38:42,920 --> 00:38:43,920
No one will know

641
00:38:44,480 --> 00:38:45,519
you're the greatest literary giant

642
00:38:45,880 --> 00:38:48,280
in the world.

643
00:38:49,360 --> 00:38:50,480
I'd better drink some tea.

644
00:38:51,599 --> 00:38:52,239
Mom!

645
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:55,000
When can I leave?

646
00:38:56,840 --> 00:38:57,800
Fan Ruoruo alone

647
00:38:57,880 --> 00:38:59,119
is already hard to deal with.

648
00:38:59,760 --> 00:39:01,719
It appears that Fan Xian is also cunning.

649
00:39:01,960 --> 00:39:03,119
Can't you focus here?

650
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:05,960
There's nothing to be focused on!

651
00:39:06,480 --> 00:39:07,199
He's just

652
00:39:07,199 --> 00:39:09,280
a bastard son from Danzhou.

653
00:39:09,960 --> 00:39:10,480
If he behaves improperly,

654
00:39:10,519 --> 00:39:11,840
a good beating will do him good.

655
00:39:13,280 --> 00:39:14,480
We can't beat him at home.

656
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:15,440
Well,

657
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:18,079
I'll ask him out for lunch tomorrow.

658
00:39:18,239 --> 00:39:19,840
Then I'll beat him up on the street.

659
00:39:20,199 --> 00:39:20,880
How do you like that?

660
00:39:22,039 --> 00:39:23,199
Breaking tricks with pure force.

661
00:39:23,559 --> 00:39:24,760
That's sort of a plan.

662
00:39:26,280 --> 00:39:26,800
Mom!

663
00:39:28,320 --> 00:39:29,840
To trick him out for lunch,

664
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:31,679
I'll need money for support.

665
00:39:32,559 --> 00:39:33,239
Support! Support!

666
00:39:36,599 --> 00:39:38,679
My Lady, Master's back.

667
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:40,400
He asks Young Master Fan Xian to see him in his study.

668
00:39:42,079 --> 00:39:42,880
Keep this for me for a while.

669
00:39:43,239 --> 00:39:44,280
I was wondering

670
00:39:44,280 --> 00:39:45,599
what's the drumstick about.

671
00:39:45,599 --> 00:39:46,360
I'll tell you everything later.

672
00:39:56,400 --> 00:39:58,519
Master wants to see Fan Xian right when he's back?

673
00:39:59,239 --> 00:40:00,239
Yes, Madam.

674
00:40:00,599 --> 00:40:02,480
It's no big deal.

675
00:40:04,840 --> 00:40:05,800
Keep watching.

676
00:40:06,559 --> 00:40:07,039
Yes.

677
00:40:10,079 --> 00:40:11,440
Your father's attitude to Fan Xian

678
00:40:11,440 --> 00:40:12,199
is of key importance.

679
00:40:12,440 --> 00:40:13,320
Mom!

680
00:40:13,639 --> 00:40:15,440
What attitude?

681
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:16,920
He left Fan Xian in Danzhou

682
00:40:16,920 --> 00:40:17,719
for so many years.

683
00:40:17,760 --> 00:40:19,320
Did he ever go back to visit him?

684
00:40:19,639 --> 00:40:21,119
That's the weirdest part.

685
00:40:22,320 --> 00:40:24,440
Your father is not a cold man.

686
00:40:24,880 --> 00:40:26,320
If he visited Fan Xian

687
00:40:26,320 --> 00:40:27,239
in Danzhou occasionally,

688
00:40:27,679 --> 00:40:28,639
I wouldn't be so nervous.

689
00:40:29,079 --> 00:40:30,039
But he just left him there

690
00:40:30,159 --> 00:40:31,119
and ignored him.

691
00:40:31,559 --> 00:40:32,960
It doesn't make sense.

692
00:40:33,960 --> 00:40:35,000
So I sent someone

693
00:40:35,000 --> 00:40:36,119
to watch Fan Xian in Danzhou.

694
00:40:36,800 --> 00:40:39,440
I just want to know

695
00:40:39,960 --> 00:40:41,320
whether he contacted Fan Xian secretly or not.

696
00:40:41,679 --> 00:40:42,400
I find it weird

697
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:43,880
all the time.

698
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:52,880
I can't protect you

699
00:40:52,880 --> 00:40:53,920
for a lifetime.

700
00:40:54,639 --> 00:40:56,239
You have to rely on yourself eventually.

701
00:40:57,280 --> 00:40:59,119
As to your future, I...

702
00:40:59,719 --> 00:41:01,559
Money! How much will you give me?

703
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:03,079
Not a dime!

704
00:41:06,000 --> 00:41:07,760
No money! Then I can't beat him.

705
00:41:08,599 --> 00:41:09,480
I can't! I can't!

706
00:41:17,440 --> 00:41:18,920
Master said you could go in

707
00:41:19,239 --> 00:41:20,440
without reporting.

708
00:42:04,800 --> 00:42:05,559
Close the door.

709
00:42:47,599 --> 00:42:48,159
Madam.

710
00:42:48,559 --> 00:42:49,400
Still inside?

711
00:42:50,000 --> 00:42:50,480
Yes.

712
00:42:50,719 --> 00:42:52,760
There's no sound. It's very quiet.

713
00:42:57,679 --> 00:43:00,599
Sizhe! Sizhe!

714
00:43:01,719 --> 00:43:02,199
Wake up!

715
00:43:03,519 --> 00:43:05,280
Mom, ten taels of silver will be enough!

716
00:43:05,480 --> 00:43:05,840
You...

717
00:43:07,679 --> 00:43:09,519
It's improper for me to go.

718
00:43:10,079 --> 00:43:11,960
Just go to your father's study.

719
00:43:12,719 --> 00:43:13,760
Say that

720
00:43:14,039 --> 00:43:15,360
you're worried that he might be hungry.

721
00:43:15,599 --> 00:43:16,880
Ask him if he wants any pastries.

722
00:43:17,719 --> 00:43:18,599
Take the chance to see

723
00:43:18,840 --> 00:43:19,920
what Fan Xian is doing

724
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:21,280
in the study.

725
00:43:25,119 --> 00:43:26,920
Mother, you're right.

726
00:43:27,400 --> 00:43:29,280
I'll do as you command.

727
00:43:32,440 --> 00:43:33,480
Take Young Master there.

728
00:43:33,960 --> 00:43:34,440
Yes.

729
00:43:46,480 --> 00:43:47,760
So obedient.

730
00:43:48,400 --> 00:43:50,320
He's finally made some progress.

731
00:43:51,360 --> 00:43:52,320
Lead the way faster!

732
00:43:52,840 --> 00:43:53,360
Yes.

733
00:43:53,480 --> 00:43:55,599
It's so late, but my dad hasn't eaten anything yet.

734
00:43:55,920 --> 00:43:57,880
I'm so worried!

735
00:43:59,599 --> 00:44:00,639
Really worried!

736
00:44:00,920 --> 00:44:01,639
Young Master?

737
00:44:02,440 --> 00:44:03,480
Am I silly?

738
00:44:03,480 --> 00:44:04,159
Young Master?

739
00:44:05,480 --> 00:44:07,039
Madam, Young Master has run away.

740
00:44:37,119 --> 00:44:37,880
Feeling anxious after waiting so long?

741
00:44:40,599 --> 00:44:42,239
Father, good evening!

742
00:44:46,119 --> 00:44:47,760
To answer your question, I'm not anxious.

743
00:44:50,039 --> 00:44:51,280
After waiting in Danzhou for so many years,

744
00:44:51,800 --> 00:44:52,639
no need to be anxious for a little longer.

745
00:44:55,360 --> 00:44:57,039
It sounds like a complaint.

746
00:44:57,960 --> 00:44:59,880
Should I shed tears

747
00:45:00,039 --> 00:45:01,679
and cry for an hour with you in my arms

748
00:45:01,800 --> 00:45:02,559
to express

749
00:45:02,559 --> 00:45:03,760
my regret?

750
00:45:03,760 --> 00:45:04,360
Please don't!

751
00:45:04,360 --> 00:45:05,280
I think so, too.

752
00:45:07,559 --> 00:45:08,639
Then let's get down to business.

753
00:45:10,679 --> 00:45:12,079
What kind of person do you want to become?

754
00:45:14,440 --> 00:45:16,880
I want to become the richest man in the world,

755
00:45:17,239 --> 00:45:18,920
living a peaceful and romantic life
with many young and beautiful wives.

756
00:45:19,920 --> 00:45:21,719
Sorry, I'm a vulgar man.

757
00:45:21,840 --> 00:45:23,079
How will you build up a fortune?

758
00:45:23,199 --> 00:45:24,440
I've already thought about that!

759
00:45:25,639 --> 00:45:26,920
I have a unique technique.

760
00:45:27,360 --> 00:45:28,559
Under high temperatures,

761
00:45:28,719 --> 00:45:30,920
I can make something marvelous out of sands

762
00:45:31,199 --> 00:45:32,960
which is much smoother and
more transparent than the crystal.

763
00:45:33,440 --> 00:45:34,400
I call it glass.

764
00:45:34,559 --> 00:45:35,800
Once it is made...

765
00:45:41,960 --> 00:45:43,000
Where did you get that?

766
00:45:43,360 --> 00:45:45,039
Your mom made it before.

767
00:45:45,400 --> 00:45:48,079
And the technique is mature.

768
00:45:51,679 --> 00:45:53,400
Never mind. I've got something else.

769
00:45:54,000 --> 00:45:54,960
I can use grease

770
00:45:55,079 --> 00:45:56,360
to produce something special

771
00:45:56,360 --> 00:45:57,360
which can clean both clothes and human body.

772
00:45:57,360 --> 00:45:58,880
Smooth as grease

773
00:45:58,880 --> 00:45:59,679
with fragrance,

774
00:45:59,920 --> 00:46:01,719
it's far better than honey locust and wood ash.

775
00:46:01,840 --> 00:46:03,079
I call it soap.

776
00:46:12,360 --> 00:46:14,039
Your mom made it before.

777
00:46:14,519 --> 00:46:15,440
She not only made soap,

778
00:46:16,039 --> 00:46:16,960
but also perfumed soap.

779
00:46:18,159 --> 00:46:18,840
That's fine.

780
00:46:18,920 --> 00:46:20,280
Actually, I've got something else.

781
00:46:20,719 --> 00:46:21,480
Nowadays,

782
00:46:21,480 --> 00:46:22,400
besides honey,

783
00:46:22,400 --> 00:46:23,199
sweet food are usually made of

784
00:46:23,280 --> 00:46:24,280
maltose or malt.

785
00:46:24,480 --> 00:46:26,159
Even saccharose is pretty rough.

786
00:46:26,199 --> 00:46:26,800
I've got a technique

787
00:46:26,920 --> 00:46:28,480
to further refine the saccharose into

788
00:46:28,559 --> 00:46:30,119
granulated sugar as white as snow.

789
00:46:30,119 --> 00:46:31,159
And the flavor is excellent.

790
00:46:31,360 --> 00:46:32,320
White granulated sugar.

791
00:46:32,719 --> 00:46:34,280
There are two full jars in the kitchen.

792
00:46:36,199 --> 00:46:37,719
Also made by my mom?

793
00:46:37,960 --> 00:46:40,440
Yes, your mom made it back then.

794
00:46:40,440 --> 00:46:41,559
Why haven't I seen these things

795
00:46:41,559 --> 00:46:42,599
in Danzhou?

796
00:46:42,719 --> 00:46:43,840
They are only used by

797
00:46:44,119 --> 00:46:45,400
influential officials

798
00:46:45,559 --> 00:46:47,880
and circulated in big cities.

799
00:46:49,320 --> 00:46:50,320
So I'm to blame

800
00:46:50,320 --> 00:46:51,039
for living in the rural area.

801
00:46:52,039 --> 00:46:53,599
Do you have any other ideas?

802
00:47:00,800 --> 00:47:01,280
No.

803
00:47:03,360 --> 00:47:05,360
Why is my mom always one step ahead of me?!

804
00:47:08,159 --> 00:47:09,239
Your mom ran a firm,

805
00:47:09,519 --> 00:47:11,199
so she had countless fancy ideas.

806
00:47:11,719 --> 00:47:12,960
Back then, the scale of her firm

807
00:47:13,960 --> 00:47:15,039
was already No.1

808
00:47:15,199 --> 00:47:17,239
in the world.

809
00:47:17,800 --> 00:47:20,159
It was the fortune center of the world.

810
00:47:20,400 --> 00:47:21,159
I've heard about that.

811
00:47:21,760 --> 00:47:22,960
Rumor has it that after she died,

812
00:47:23,320 --> 00:47:24,519
the firm was registered under the state treasury.

813
00:47:24,639 --> 00:47:25,679
That's not true.

814
00:47:26,159 --> 00:47:27,719
It was controlled by the imperial family

815
00:47:27,920 --> 00:47:29,519
and was named Neiku
(Homophone for underwear in Chinese).

816
00:47:32,039 --> 00:47:33,639
Who came up with such a vulgar name?

817
00:47:33,760 --> 00:47:34,559
Mind your words!

818
00:47:35,840 --> 00:47:37,800
It was named by His Majesty.

819
00:47:40,280 --> 00:47:42,679
What's so vulgar?

820
00:47:44,519 --> 00:47:46,360
Never mind. Go on.

821
00:47:47,599 --> 00:47:50,159
Diligent in handling complicated national affairs,

822
00:47:50,400 --> 00:47:52,079
His Majesty has no energy

823
00:47:52,159 --> 00:47:53,480
to manage Neiku in person.

824
00:47:53,800 --> 00:47:54,400
Therefore,

825
00:47:55,360 --> 00:47:56,920
he put Li Yunrui, the Princess Royal,

826
00:47:57,119 --> 00:47:59,159
in charge.

827
00:48:01,119 --> 00:48:02,559
The Princess Royal is in charge of Neiku?

828
00:48:11,360 --> 00:48:13,760
She's extremely beautiful

829
00:48:14,039 --> 00:48:15,360
and very gentle.

830
00:48:15,920 --> 00:48:17,880
Though she's not related to His Majesty by blood,

831
00:48:18,400 --> 00:48:19,679
she's deeply trusted.

832
00:48:20,079 --> 00:48:23,239
And she's not married yet.

833
00:48:43,760 --> 00:48:44,480
Father,

834
00:48:45,719 --> 00:48:47,440
are you into her?

835
00:48:48,000 --> 00:48:49,000
Nonsense!

836
00:48:49,360 --> 00:48:50,400
Since we met,

837
00:48:50,920 --> 00:48:52,719
you've talked from the firm to the Princess Royal.

838
00:48:53,159 --> 00:48:54,440
You said we would talk about business,

839
00:48:54,599 --> 00:48:55,920
but you only talked about gossips.

840
00:48:57,039 --> 00:48:58,400
Do you know what gossip means?

841
00:48:58,800 --> 00:48:59,880
The Princess Royal

842
00:49:00,039 --> 00:49:02,440
has a daughter with Lin Ruofu,

843
00:49:03,119 --> 00:49:04,119
the current Prime Minister.

844
00:49:04,960 --> 00:49:06,039
You just said

845
00:49:06,400 --> 00:49:07,320
she's not married yet.

846
00:49:07,480 --> 00:49:09,679
It's a big secret.

847
00:49:10,360 --> 00:49:11,559
You're definitely gossiping!

848
00:49:13,000 --> 00:49:14,360
The Princess Royal's daughter

849
00:49:14,719 --> 00:49:16,440
