902
00:51:16,679 --> 00:51:18,119
She has no say

903
00:51:18,639 --> 00:51:19,440
in your marriage with Lin Wan'er.

904
00:51:19,719 --> 00:51:20,719
She's her mom, yet she has no say in this?

905
00:51:20,840 --> 00:51:21,880
For the imperial family,

906
00:51:22,280 --> 00:51:23,719
family affection is never the theme.

907
00:51:24,000 --> 00:51:27,079
You want to stop Fan Xian from marrying Wan'er?

908
00:51:29,880 --> 00:51:31,079
Your Majesty, I beg your support!

909
00:51:47,239 --> 00:51:48,079
The Princess Royal

910
00:51:51,280 --> 00:51:51,960
Eunuch Hong,

911
00:51:52,840 --> 00:51:53,599
I'm sorry.

912
00:52:07,920 --> 00:52:08,880
When it comes to the imperial family,

913
00:52:09,280 --> 00:52:11,920
