As long as His Majesty consents,

919
00:52:31,480 --> 00:52:32,960
what others think

920
00:52:33,159 --> 00:52:34,000
doesn't matter.

921
00:52:34,679 --> 00:52:35,679
But why does His Majesty

922
00:52:35,679 --> 00:52:36,519
have to make me

923
00:52:36,519 --> 00:52:37,440
marry Lin Wan'er?

924
00:52:37,719 --> 00:52:39,239
His Majesty has four sons.

925
00:52:39,719 --> 00:52:41,119
The eldest one is away leading troops.

926
00:52:41,119 --> 00:52:42,480
The youngest one is still a child.

927
00:52:42,960 --> 00:52:45,119
Now the Crown Prince and the second prince

928
00:52:45,960 --> 00:52:48,039
are fighting for the throne.

929
00:52:48,599 --> 00:52:49,800
How is that relevant to me?

930
00:52:50,239 --> 00:52:52,760
The Princess Royal has supported

931
00:52:52,880 --> 00:52:54,039
the Crown Prince all along.

932
00:52:55,639 --> 00:52:56,559
