It's probable with interests concerned.

944
00:53:22,079 --> 00:53:23,199
You've said all these

945
00:53:23,400 --> 00:53:24,719
to clear

946
00:53:25,159 --> 00:53:26,039
Liu Ruyu.

947
00:53:27,480 --> 00:53:28,119
You don't believe me?

948
00:53:28,440 --> 00:53:29,920
You even drag the Crown Prince into this.

949
00:53:30,400 --> 00:53:31,280
Does it matter if I believe you or not?

950
00:53:35,480 --> 00:53:36,039
Follow me.

951
00:53:51,880 --> 00:53:52,400
I'm hungry.

952
00:53:59,840 --> 00:54:01,480
Finished talking? Go ahead and take a seat.

