956
00:54:19,480 --> 00:54:21,719
We have important things to discuss. Please leave us.

957
00:54:30,119 --> 00:54:30,639
Yes.

958
00:54:33,239 --> 00:54:34,239
Only me?

959
00:54:45,679 --> 00:54:46,679
Get out now!

960
00:54:46,840 --> 00:54:47,199
Yes.

961
00:54:50,519 --> 00:54:51,519
Did you send

962
