Butler Zhou to Danzhou?

963
00:54:57,320 --> 00:54:58,559
Master, you've known that.

964
00:55:00,079 --> 00:55:01,400
Danzhou is so faraway.

965
00:55:01,800 --> 00:55:02,719
I thought

966
00:55:02,760 --> 00:55:04,599
it would be reassuring to send someone trustworthy

967
00:55:04,920 --> 00:55:06,039
to take care of Xian'er.

968
00:55:06,039 --> 00:55:07,440
He tried to assassinate Fan Xian

969
00:55:08,079 --> 00:55:09,519
in Danzhou.

970
00:55:11,320 --> 00:55:12,840
A...assassinate?!

971
00:55:12,960 --> 00:55:13,679
You don't know that?

972
00:55:14,519 --> 00:55:16,079
I haven't heard from him this month.

973
00:55:16,800 --> 00:55:17,519
I've no idea.

974
00:55:17,599 --> 00:55:18,599
There won't be any letters.

975
00:55:19,519 --> 00:55:21,239
My mother has sent him onto a fish boat.

976
00:55:21,400 --> 00:55:23,360
He won't get down in recent years.

977
00:55:26,440 --> 00:55:27,840
Staying away for all these years,

978
00:55:28,960 --> 00:55:30,880
he actually dare betray his master.

979
00:55:32,440 --> 00:55:33,760
Thank God Xian'er is all right.

980
00:55:35,960 --> 00:55:37,599
Butler Zhou confessed it all.

981
00:55:38,360 --> 00:55:39,880
He had received your secret letter,

982
00:55:41,199 --> 00:55:43,559
asking him to kill Fan Xian

983
00:55:43,920 --> 00:55:45,719
with the Investigator's Office.

984
00:55:46,800 --> 00:55:47,840
How come the Investigator's Office is also involved?

985
00:55:47,920 --> 00:55:50,840
They also received a fake order.

986
00:55:51,159 --> 00:55:53,199
The Investigator's Office only answers to His Majesty.

987
00:55:53,599 --> 00:55:55,480
Whoever can insert spies in the Investigator's Office

988
00:55:56,079 --> 00:55:57,639
must be from the imperial family.

989
00:55:58,280 --> 00:56:00,960
And Lady Yi, mother of the youngest prince,

990
00:56:03,360 --> 00:56:04,599
