991
00:56:05,519 --> 00:56:06,960
Master, you mean

992
00:56:06,960 --> 00:56:08,119
I am the one who wants to kill Fan Xian?

993
00:56:08,159 --> 00:56:08,800
Aren't you?

994
00:56:09,400 --> 00:56:09,960
No, it's not me.

995
00:56:09,960 --> 00:56:11,079
Why not?

996
00:56:11,320 --> 00:56:11,719
I...

997
00:56:11,960 --> 00:56:12,800
Tell him.

998
00:56:21,760 --> 00:56:22,719
If I want to kill you,

999
00:56:23,079 --> 00:56:23,960
I'll definitely

1000
00:56:23,960 --> 00:56:24,960
find a stranger

1001
00:56:24,960 --> 00:56:25,519
to do the job.

1002
00:56:25,800 --> 00:56:27,320
I'll never ask Butler Zhou to do it.

1003
00:56:28,079 --> 00:56:29,360
I... I'm not that stupid.

1004
00:56:29,639 --> 00:56:31,039
Maybe you did it the opposite way.

1005
00:56:31,320 --> 00:56:32,559
I have no reason to kill you.

1006
00:56:32,559 --> 00:56:33,800
You don't want me to inherit the family properties.

1007
00:56:34,079 --> 00:56:35,039
No, Fan Xian.

1008
00:56:35,199 --> 00:56:36,239
I might be particular about you,

1009
00:56:36,400 --> 00:56:37,360
and I might try to suppress you,

1010
00:56:37,639 --> 00:56:38,719
but I'll never try to kill you.

1011
00:56:38,719 --> 00:56:39,159
Why?

1012
00:56:39,599 --> 00:56:40,719
If you die because of me,

1013
00:56:40,960 --> 00:56:42,480
Master is sure to

1014
00:56:42,559 --> 00:56:43,960
drive Sizhe and me out of the Fan mansion.

1015
00:56:45,920 --> 00:56:46,320
I...

1016
00:56:46,880 --> 00:56:47,280
This...

1017
00:56:48,880 --> 00:56:49,320
Ruoruo.

1018
00:56:49,360 --> 00:56:50,400
I think she's made a point.

1019
00:56:51,400 --> 00:56:52,880
If she wanted to kill you,

1020
00:56:53,760 --> 00:56:54,920
she wouldn't involve her minion.

1021
00:56:55,840 --> 00:56:56,480
Right.

1022
00:57:00,320 --> 00:57:00,960
So?

1023
00:57:02,000 --> 00:57:02,920
Words alone

1024
00:57:02,920 --> 00:57:03,800
can't prove anything.

1025
00:57:04,440 --> 00:57:04,880
I...

1026
00:57:06,039 --> 00:57:07,239
You can investigate on your own.

1027
00:57:08,360 --> 00:57:09,239
Let's eat first.

1028
00:57:20,039 --> 00:57:20,960
Father,

1029
00:57:22,079 --> 00:57:22,880
I'm leaving for studying.

1030
00:57:23,960 --> 00:57:24,960
Me, too.

1031
00:57:28,679 --> 00:57:29,199
Yes.

1032
00:57:37,280 --> 00:57:37,840
Master,

1033
00:57:38,360 --> 00:57:39,159
the room for Xian'er

1034
00:57:39,360 --> 00:57:41,119
is tidied up.

1035
00:57:41,280 --> 00:57:42,280
I'd like to show him around now.

1036
00:57:42,280 --> 00:57:43,000
See if he needs anything else.

1037
00:57:43,480 --> 00:57:44,480
You may leave first.

1038
00:57:45,159 --> 00:57:45,960
I need a word

1039
00:57:45,960 --> 00:57:47,159
with him.

1040
00:57:48,599 --> 00:57:49,079
Yes.

1041
00:58:01,320 --> 00:58:02,280
You're in the capital city now.

1042
00:58:02,599 --> 00:58:03,719
Learn to be cautious

1043
00:58:04,880 --> 00:58:06,199
