1052
00:58:30,119 --> 00:58:30,599
What's this?

1053
00:58:30,880 --> 00:58:31,880
Arrest warrant.

1054
00:58:32,480 --> 00:58:34,039
I found it in the files of the Ministry of Penalty.

1055
00:58:44,039 --> 00:58:45,119
It's for Teng Zijing.

1056
00:58:46,039 --> 00:58:46,840
What crime did he commit?

1057
00:58:47,079 --> 00:58:48,639
I don't know, and I don't need to know.

1058
00:58:48,880 --> 00:58:50,039
Just be careful of him.

1059
00:58:54,760 --> 00:58:56,239
It's an old warrant.

1060
00:58:56,280 --> 00:58:57,800
Anyway, he's not here now.

1061
00:58:59,199 --> 00:59:00,960
Stay away from the Investigator's Office

1062
00:59:01,639 --> 00:59:03,599
