1090
01:00:17,880 --> 01:00:18,559
I've told you.

1091
01:00:19,239 --> 01:00:21,000
It's the best chance to get back

1092
01:00:21,400 --> 01:00:22,440
your mom's properties

1093
01:00:23,440 --> 01:00:24,320
You're right.

1094
01:00:24,400 --> 01:00:24,960
Well.

1095
01:00:25,719 --> 01:00:27,960
You're also tired. Have a good rest.

1096
01:00:34,320 --> 01:00:35,920
As to your marriage with Lin Wan'er,

1097
01:00:36,679 --> 01:00:37,719
I'll arrange everything for you.

1098
01:00:37,800 --> 01:00:39,159
No need to worry about anything.

1099
01:00:39,840 --> 01:00:40,440
I don't want to marry her.

1100
01:00:43,320 --> 01:00:43,960
What did you say?

1101
01:00:44,400 --> 01:00:44,960
I said

1102
01:00:45,760 --> 01:00:47,320
I didn't want to marry Lin Wan'er.

1103
01:00:48,079 --> 01:00:49,639
I've said so much,

1104
01:00:50,280 --> 01:00:51,519
but you still don't get it?

1105
01:00:51,599 --> 01:00:52,519
I get it.

1106
01:00:54,079 --> 01:00:55,639
My mom used to have a firm.

1107
01:00:56,000 --> 01:00:56,559
Now it belongs

1108
01:00:56,559 --> 01:00:57,760
to the imperial family.

1109
01:00:58,519 --> 01:00:59,599
By marrying Lin Wan'er,

1110
01:00:59,679 --> 01:01:00,760
I can take the firm back.

1111
01:01:00,840 --> 01:01:02,119
Now is the perfect chance.

1112
01:01:02,280 --> 01:01:04,000
I understand all the things you've said.

1113
01:01:04,320 --> 01:01:05,800
I just don't want to marry her.

1114
01:01:06,000 --> 01:01:06,599
Why?

1115
01:01:07,159 --> 01:01:07,840
I'm falling in love with

1116
01:01:07,840 --> 01:01:08,760
a drumstick thief.

1117
01:01:09,519 --> 01:01:10,000
What's this?

1118
01:01:11,119 --> 01:01:12,559
Actually, it has nothing to do with her.

1119
01:01:13,239 --> 01:01:14,599
Even if I hadn't met her,

1120
01:01:14,800 --> 01:01:16,119
I still won't marry Lin Wan'er.

1121
01:01:16,760 --> 01:01:17,880
Neiku is the fruit of

1122
01:01:17,880 --> 01:01:20,119
your mom's painstaking labor for a lifetime.

1123
01:01:20,119 --> 01:01:22,400
I understand it's very important to you.

1124
01:01:26,679 --> 01:01:27,199
But...

1125
01:01:27,559 --> 01:01:28,440
But how can I

1126
01:01:28,519 --> 01:01:29,599
put this?

1127
01:01:34,679 --> 01:01:35,920
Look!

1128
01:01:38,239 --> 01:01:38,960
It can move.
